fields.name: Umeqo Consulting Panel
fields.description:
Are you interested in launching a career in consulting? Join Umeqo consultants and recruiters for a careers presentation and interactive panel discussion. Attendees will learn about:

• Accenture business areas

• Career paths and development

• Company culture, values, and commitment to corporate citizenship

Refreshments will be served and casual attire is welcome. We look forward to seeing you there!
